{
  "texts": [
    "The maximum length of the target sequence was set to 545 tokens, which covered 95% of proteins in the datasets, and the same max protein sequence lengths of previous studies [29,43].",
    "Interaction prediction headThe class tokens of drug and target sequences have abstract meanings for each sequence.",
    "The interaction prediction head aggregated the features of drug-target pairs and predicted binding probability.",
    "In this step, there were multiple choices for mixing the features; for example, cross attention, capsule network, etc.",
    "However, we simply employed concatenation that showed stable performances in the previous work [43].The interaction module consists of three sequential blocks."
  ]
}